response.original_title: Doctor Catgari and the Duck of Doom
response.overview: It was a quiet day in Steampark Omni, a young girl quietly feeding the ducks, that is, until a dark figure approaches. Dr Catgari takes notice of the girl, but upon his advances the ducks attack. Undaunted Dr Catgari heads to his lab to create a weapon of dastardly duck destruct
response.title: Doctor Catgari and the Duck of Doom
